{
  "info": {
    "name": "Bazar Management API",
    "description": "Colección para probar la API del bazar (Cliente, Producto, Venta).\n\nFlujo sugerido end-to-end:\n1) Crear cliente  2) Crear producto  3) Crear venta (descuenta stock)\n4) Ver producto (stock bajó)  5) Cancelar venta (stock vuelve)\n\nLos POST de creación guardan automáticamente el id en variables de colección ({{clienteId}}, {{productoId}}, {{ventaId}}).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8081/api/v1" },
    { "key": "clienteId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "productoId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "ventaId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Flujo E2E (Runner)",
      "description": "Corré SOLO esta carpeta en el Collection Runner. Los requests están en orden de ejecución y validan el ciclo completo: crear -> vender -> stock baja -> cancelar -> stock vuelve -> soft-delete -> bloqueos -> reactivar.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Crear producto (stock 100)",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
            "var b = pm.response.json();",
            "pm.collectionVariables.set('productoId', b.id);",
            "pm.test('nace ACTIVO', () => pm.expect(b.estado).to.eql('ACTIVO'));",
            "pm.test('stock 100', () => pm.expect(b.cantidadDisponible).to.eql(100));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Teclado\",\n  \"marca\": \"Logitech\",\n  \"costo\": 25.50,\n  \"cantidadDisponible\": 100\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/productos", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["productos"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Crear cliente",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
            "var b = pm.response.json();",
            "pm.collectionVariables.set('clienteId', b.id);",
            "pm.test('nace ACTIVO', () => pm.expect(b.estado).to.eql('ACTIVO'));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Juan\",\n  \"apellido\": \"Perez\",\n  \"dni\": \"12345678\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/clientes", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["clientes"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Crear venta (cantidad 2)",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
            "var b = pm.response.json();",
            "pm.collectionVariables.set('ventaId', b.id);",
            "pm.test('estado ACTIVA', () => pm.expect(b.estado).to.eql('ACTIVA'));",
            "pm.test('tiene 1 detalle', () => pm.expect(b.detalles.length).to.eql(1));",
            "pm.test('total = 51', () => pm.expect(b.total).to.eql(51.0));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"clienteId\": {{clienteId}},\n  \"items\": [\n    { \"productoId\": {{productoId}}, \"cantidad\": 2 }\n  ]\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/ventas", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["ventas"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Verificar stock descontado (98)",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('stock = 98', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().cantidadDisponible).to.eql(98));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/productos/{{productoId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["productos", "{{productoId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Cancelar venta",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('estado ANULADA', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().estado).to.eql('ANULADA'));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/ventas/{{ventaId}}/cancelar", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["ventas", "{{ventaId}}", "cancelar"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "6. Verificar stock repuesto (100)",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('stock = 100', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().cantidadDisponible).to.eql(100));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/productos/{{productoId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["productos", "{{productoId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "7. Desactivar cliente (soft-delete)",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 204', () => pm.response.to.have.status(204));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["clientes", "{{clienteId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "8. Cliente NO aparece en listado activos",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "var ids = pm.response.json().map(c => c.id);",
            "pm.test('no esta el inactivo', () => pm.expect(ids).to.not.include(Number(pm.collectionVariables.get('clienteId'))));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/clientes", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["clientes"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "9. Cliente SI accesible por id (INACTIVO)",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('estado INACTIVO', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().estado).to.eql('INACTIVO'));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["clientes", "{{clienteId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "10. Vender con cliente inactivo -> 409",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 409', () => pm.response.to.have.status(409));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"clienteId\": {{clienteId}},\n  \"items\": [\n    { \"productoId\": {{productoId}}, \"cantidad\": 1 }\n  ]\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/ventas", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["ventas"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "11. Reactivar cliente",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('estado ACTIVO', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().estado).to.eql('ACTIVO'));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}/activar", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["clientes", "{{clienteId}}", "activar"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "12. Desactivar producto",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 204', () => pm.response.to.have.status(204));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/productos/{{productoId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["productos", "{{productoId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "13. Descontar stock de producto inactivo -> 409",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 409', () => pm.response.to.have.status(409));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"cantidad\": 1\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/productos/{{productoId}}/stock", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["productos", "{{productoId}}", "stock"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "14. Reactivar producto (limpieza)",
          "event": [ { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
            "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('estado ACTIVO', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().estado).to.eql('ACTIVO'));"
          ] } } ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/productos/{{productoId}}/activar", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["productos", "{{productoId}}", "activar"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
